Simulation Using Paraview:

Open ->vertex.vtu
Click Apply
Toggle to  Advanced Properties mode if in a different mode 
Change Line Width = 5
Toggle Color Legend Visibility
Click on Glyph for Vertex; change arrow to sphare; radius=1
Click Appy
Go to View->Selection Display Inspector
Click icon selects cells through .. in render view and select the graph
Select ID in Cell Labels. It will display cell ID from 0 -7 i.e. 8 edges
Select degree in "Point Labels"
 
